    "display_name": "Fashion Tech Journalist",
    "long_instructions": "## Maya Singh, Fashion Technology Journalist\r\n\r\n**Location:** London, UK\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Fashion & Tech Magazine\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Wearable technology, AI in retail, trend analysis\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"I cover how innovations like AR Mirrors are reshaping the industry. From virtual fitting rooms to AI-driven styling suggestions, this technology is revolutionizing the way we shop.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
